<br>
Part of this kids punishment should be programming a firewall to help stop people like him from getting into the system, but no matter what programs are written, there will always be a way around it.  <br>
<br>
For all of you who have no FIREWALL protection on your personal computers.  Check out Zonealert.  It is a FREE download.  I will not give the address to it since many people would not trust it from me since you do not know me.  If any of you go to the EQATLAS.COM site, this firewall protection link is on there near the bottom of the home page.  It will alert you to any IP address that sends information to your IP address and stop any program from sending information from your IP address to any other address, and ask you first.  You can allow any of the programs to send information that one time, or 100% of the time.  Another cool feature is when your screen saver comes on you can have it totally stop any information from being sent OR received, a great item for people like me that have cable/DSL always on type connections.  Another program (more features, but you pay money for it is BLACKICE.)   Well, enough free advertising...just thought you all could use the info. <p><B><I> Taek Lichsummoner <BR> 
